data.eml:eml: Notes on Mesocapromys sanfelipensis (Rodentia: Capromyidae) from Cuba

This dataset contains the digitized treatments in Plazi based on the original journal article Viñola López, Lazaro W., Garrido, Orlando H., Bermúdez, Alberto (2018): Notes on Mesocapromys sanfelipensis (Rodentia: Capromyidae) from Cuba. Zootaxa 4410 (1): 164-176, DOI: https://doi.org/10.11646/zootaxa.4410.1.9
